that we're despicable,
that we're small.

00:27:53.470 --> 00:27:57.770 align:middle line:84%
And when we buy that, as we're
powerful, creative beings,

00:27:57.770 --> 00:27:58.903 align:middle line:90%
we make it so.

00:27:58.903 --> 00:28:00.070 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: We do make it so.

00:28:00.070 --> 00:28:00.980 align:middle line:90%
>> MONTANA: We make it so.

00:28:00.980 --> 00:28:03.400 align:middle line:84%
>> REGINA: And every time we
