and thoughts

00:28:10.510 --> 00:28:12.890 align:middle line:84%
that are repeated
throughout the day,

00:28:12.890 --> 00:28:15.380 align:middle line:84%
every day that become
the quality of our lives.

00:28:15.380 --> 00:28:16.180 align:middle line:90%
>> MONTANA: Yeah.

00:28:16.180 --> 00:28:17.650 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: And we know.

00:28:17.650 --> 00:28:20.866 align:middle line:90%
We've been-- I was a New Ager.

