Start judging them to
somehow make yourself

00:28:41.110 --> 00:28:43.540 align:middle line:84%
feel superior in some
teensy, little way

00:28:43.540 --> 00:28:47.200 align:middle line:84%
in this competitive environment
that you're talking about.

00:28:47.200 --> 00:28:51.800 align:middle line:84%
And so the due diligence to
first quiet yourself like you

00:28:51.800 --> 00:28:56.570 align:middle line:84%
did, start recognizing this body
already has everything in it,

00:28:56.570 --> 00:28:57.370 align:middle line:90%
it's--

