>> MONTANA: [CHUCKLES]

00:28:58.056 --> 00:28:58.750 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: It's permeating.

00:28:58.750 --> 00:28:59.430 align:middle line:90%
>> MONTANA: This is life.

00:28:59.430 --> 00:29:01.910 align:middle line:84%
>> REGINA: All consciousness
is permeating this space that

00:29:01.910 --> 00:29:02.730 align:middle line:90%
