00:29:02.730 --> 00:29:03.240 align:middle line:90%
>> MONTANA: It's all here--

00:29:03.240 --> 00:29:05.400 align:middle line:84%
>> REGINA: And it's
accessible right here now.

00:29:05.400 --> 00:29:08.000 align:middle line:84%
And to dare to
say, wait a minute,

00:29:08.000 --> 00:29:10.670 align:middle line:84%
to yourself, why am I having
that ugly little thought

00:29:10.670 --> 00:29:11.750 align:middle line:90%
about that person?

00:29:11.750 --> 00:29:13.710 align:middle line:84%
What do I think I'm
gaining out of that?

00:29:13.710 --> 00:29:15.725 align:middle line:84%
It's going to take
that level of maturity.

00:29:15.725 --> 00:29:16.525 align:middle line:90%
>> MONTANA: Yes.

00:29:16.525 --> 00:29:18.455 align:middle line:84%
And when I look in the
