Ooh.

00:29:24.500 --> 00:29:27.590 align:middle line:84%
The horrific self-judgment
is so painful.

00:29:27.590 --> 00:29:29.960 align:middle line:84%
>> REGINA: Self-judgment, as
well as judgment of others,

00:29:29.960 --> 00:29:34.220 align:middle line:84%
they are equally devastating
to the nature of what

00:29:34.220 --> 00:29:35.495 align:middle line:90%
we're creating as our reality.

00:29:35.495 --> 00:29:37.120 align:middle line:84%
>> MONTANA: We are
so powerful, Regina,

00:29:37.120 --> 00:29:38.730 align:middle line:84%
and we don't see
what we're doing.

00:29:38.730 --> 00:29:42.080 align:middle line:84%
And every time I go outside
of myself for answers,

00:29:42.080 --> 00:29:45.980 align:middle line:84%
