00:29:51.830 --> 00:29:56.780 align:middle line:84%
And so again, the program
is to always keep us

00:29:56.780 --> 00:29:59.727 align:middle line:84%
outside of ourselves and
in a lack of self-trust.

00:29:59.727 --> 00:30:01.310 align:middle line:84%
>> REGINA: Yes, and
now we're having--

00:30:01.310 --> 00:30:04.130 align:middle line:84%
