00:30:04.130 --> 00:30:05.297 align:middle line:90%
right now because we're at--

00:30:05.297 --> 00:30:06.422 align:middle line:90%
>> MONTANA: Well, I'll say.

00:30:06.422 --> 00:30:08.210 align:middle line:84%
>> REGINA: We're at
the time of choosing,

