really at a critical
time of choosing.

00:30:09.858 --> 00:30:11.150 align:middle line:90%
>> MONTANA: Absolutely, Regina.

00:30:11.150 --> 00:30:13.610 align:middle line:84%
>> REGINA: And so now a lot
of people are choosing to take

00:30:13.610 --> 00:30:14.610 align:middle line:90%
their own lives.

00:30:14.610 --> 00:30:15.410 align:middle line:90%
>> MONTANA: Yeah.

