>> MONTANA: Good question.

00:30:49.230 --> 00:30:50.290 align:middle line:90%
Yes and no.

00:30:50.290 --> 00:30:52.830 align:middle line:84%
I think the hard part
was looking at how

00:30:52.830 --> 00:30:54.930 align:middle line:90%
screwed up everything is.

00:30:54.930 --> 00:30:58.462 align:middle line:84%
And where's the way
back from the precipice?

00:30:58.462 --> 00:31:00.893 align:middle line:84%
And for the longest
time, it was like, well,

00:31:00.893 --> 00:31:02.310 align:middle line:84%
I'm going to be a
spiritual light,

00:31:02.310 --> 00:31:04.620 align:middle line:84%
and I'm going to
help fix the planet.

00:31:04.620 --> 00:31:09.570 align:middle line:84%
And I finally gotten that
I can't fix what's broken,

00:31:09.570 --> 00:31:12.000 align:middle line:84%
and what's broken--
it's kind of like--

00:31:12.000 --> 00:31:16.410 align:middle line:84%
it's not kind of, it's totally
like, there's two paths.

00:31:16.410 --> 00:31:20.950 align:middle line:84%
There's the path where
you embrace life and align

00:31:20.950 --> 00:31:26.890 align:middle line:84%
with what is life giving and
life nurturing and sustaining--

00:31:26.890 --> 00:31:31.330 align:middle line:84%
healthy things to eat,
pharmaceuticals not to take,

00:31:31.330 --> 00:31:32.140 align:middle line:90%
certain--

00:31:32.140 --> 00:31:34.840 align:middle line:84%
you have to follow that
inner compass of what

00:31:34.840 --> 00:31:38.680 align:middle line:84%
is going to sustain
life and uplift

00:31:38.680 --> 00:31:42.490 align:middle line:84%
and make you more whole
and grounded and loving

00:31:42.490 --> 00:31:49.340 align:middle line:84%
and to not go the synthetic path
of avarice control, competition,

00:31:49.340 --> 00:31:50.150 align:middle line:90%
conflict.

00:31:50.150 --> 00:31:51.128 align:middle line:90%
It's the program.

00:31:51.128 --> 00:31:53.170 align:middle line:84%
You're either going to
buy the old program, which

00:31:53.170 --> 00:31:56.320 align:middle line:84%
is coming from society, which
is coming from religion, which

00:31:56.320 --> 00:31:58.160 align:middle line:90%
is coming from spirituality.

00:31:58.160 --> 00:31:59.560 align:middle line:84%
All those programs,
you're either

00:31:59.560 --> 00:32:04.130 align:middle line:84%
going to go that and
buy the external,

00:32:04.130 --> 00:32:06.440 align:middle line:90%
or you're going to go within.

00:32:06.440 --> 00:32:08.850 align:middle line:84%
And you're going to start
to learn to trust that.

00:32:08.850 --> 00:32:11.370 align:middle line:84%
And boy, is that a
journey to learn,

00:32:11.370 --> 00:32:14.300 align:middle line:90%
to start to trust yourself.

00:32:14.300 --> 00:32:15.930 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: And it takes time.

00:32:15.930 --> 00:32:16.830 align:middle line:90%
We're too impatient.

00:32:16.830 --> 00:32:18.222 align:middle line:90%
We want all the answers now.

00:32:18.222 --> 00:32:18.350 align:middle line:90%
>> MONTANA: Yeah.

00:32:18.350 --> 00:32:20.930 align:middle line:84%
>> REGINA: But one thing I just
heard you say that makes total

00:32:20.930 --> 00:32:21.730 align:middle line:90%
sense--

00:32:21.730 --> 00:32:24.020 align:middle line:84%
it is a life of--
we've been trained

00:32:24.020 --> 00:32:25.610 align:middle line:90%
to be consumers of everything.

00:32:25.610 --> 00:32:29.870 align:middle line:84%
We consume, take in, take in,
take in, instead of generators.

00:32:29.870 --> 00:32:32.870 align:middle line:84%
And when we start
flipping that switch

00:32:32.870 --> 00:32:36.330 align:middle line:84%
to thinking, what can I go
buy? what can I consume today?

00:32:36.330 --> 00:32:39.350 align:middle line:84%
and start thinking, What
can I generate today?

00:32:39.350 --> 00:32:40.930 align:middle line:90%
Is there something I can do?

00:32:40.930 --> 00:32:43.140 align:middle line:90%
Is there something I can give?

00:32:43.140 --> 00:32:45.650 align:middle line:84%
