bit of your self and your heart

00:32:48.290 --> 00:32:51.042 align:middle line:84%
to that person
behind the register?

00:32:51.042 --> 00:32:54.690 align:middle line:84%
That begins a generative
life, those simple steps.

00:32:54.690 --> 00:32:55.490 align:middle line:90%
>> MONTANA: Yeah.

00:32:55.490 --> 00:32:56.562 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: And so--

00:32:56.562 --> 00:32:57.770 align:middle line:90%
>> MONTANA: That's a really--

00:32:57.770 --> 00:32:59.370 align:middle line:90%
I like that, generative life.

00:32:59.370 --> 00:33:00.170 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: Mm-hmm.

