00:33:42.590 --> 00:33:43.797 align:middle line:90%
>> MONTANA: Oh.

00:33:43.797 --> 00:33:45.630 align:middle line:84%
>> REGINA: I mean, it
gives you the chills--

00:33:45.630 --> 00:33:46.020 align:middle line:90%
>> MONTANA: It does.

00:33:46.020 --> 00:33:46.920 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: --to think about it.

